The,service,from,the,U,S,National,Renewable,Energy,Laboratory,NREL,provides,access,to,a,database,of,solar,radiation,available,at,locations,within,the,United,States,The,National,Solar,Radiation,Database,NSRDB,lists,recorded,solar,energy,readings,from,a,wide,range,of,weather,stations,Data,are,summarized,based,on,readings,captured,using,the,Typical,Meteorological,Year,TMY,methodology,API,methods,support,search,for,solar,radiation,data,for,a,location,specified,by,latitude,and,longitude,Results,can,be,restricted,to,specific,fields,such,as,date,and,time,of,recordings,specific,recording,station,solar,conditions,such,as,zenith,and,illumination,and,weather,conditions,like,precipitation,and,barometric,pressure